         gir1.2-gtk-3.0,
         zenity,
         libnotify-bin,
         nemo
Recommends: zip, tar
Description: GPG encryption integration for Nemo file manager
 nemo-crypt provides seamless GPG encryption and decryption functionality
 directly in the Nemo file manager through context menu actions.
 .
 Features:
  * Right-click encryption from Nemo's context menu
  * Symmetric (passphrase) and asymmetric (public key) encryption
  * Digital signature support and verification
  * Multi-file encryption with packaging options
  * GTK3 native encryption settings dialog
  * Archive support (.zip, .tar.gz, .tar.bz2)
  * Comprehensive signature verification with detailed status
  * Security hardening and error handling
